name: Cheems
description: Cheems is the first real memecoin ever created on Solana, inspired by a world-famous meme, airdropped in May 2021. One of the most famous memes on earth, named a "Meme of the Year" in 2021 by Know Your Meme. This viral Shiba Inu, known for humorous misspellings like "Cheemsburger," has gained massive popularity on social media with high engagement across platforms. This dog appears in various memes such as "Swole Doge vs. Cheems," "Bonk," "Godzilla and King Kong," and in the Spanish-speaking regions as "No puede ser" and "Me da ansiedad," showcasing its versatility in different humorous contexts. Its influence extends beyond digital, inspiring merchandise and being shared by celebrities and influencers like elon musk.
